Looking for people to beta test an hourly billing virtual machine platform. Probably test will be with $10.00 credit.

&lt;b&gt;Features&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create/destroy virtual machines on the fly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Upload and mount your own ISO files&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;KVM virtualization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Snapshots (currently not working for large VM's, so only for 512 MB, 15 GB disk machines) for backup and/or templates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private IP address for 1gbps+ communication between VMs (1gbps in Chicago, may be faster in Scranton)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;API (soon)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

PM if interested (include email address).
